dct_title_s: Suburban street map of metropolitan Wollongong
dct_description_sm: Inset map of town center. Map includes index to suburbs and other features. Map shows suburb & locality boundaries, two classes of roads, railways, and road distance from Wollongong.
dct_creator_sm: Gregory's Guides and Maps, Pty. Ltd
